original_title: Prototype I: Quantum Leaps in Trans Semiotics through Psycho-Analytical Snail Serum
overview: The first of a trilogy set in the Interbau Project in Berlin, drawing on a wide range of feminist perspectives within queer theory, psychoanalysis, quantum physics, genetics, cybernetics and systems biology.
title: Prototype I: Quantum Leaps in Trans Semiotics through Psycho-Analytical Snail Serum
